<p><strong>Feedback Forum</strong></p>

<p>Each meeting includes Feedback Forum (30 min feedback sessions). A participant shares a segment of &lt;2000 words; other participants comments for 20 min in Google docs &amp; 10 min verbally <a href="https://twitter.com/DarbyVickers/status/1387089114852249604">Idea Source</a></p>

